text: Khushab is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Khushab may also refer to: *Khushab District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan) *Khushab Tehsil, a tehsil of district Khushab *Khushab Junction railway station, a railway station in Punjab region. ==See also== *Khushab Nuclear Complex, a plutonium production complex. *Khvoshab (disambiguation), several places in Iran * *
title: Khushab (disambiguation)
